commit.message: Add files via upload
Merge remote-tracking branch 'refs/remotes/origin/master'

Fixing auto-update to work with the latest sourceforge web design, and
https support.

Update Compiling.md

Updated msys2 windows build instructions based on my experience with latest msys2

Merge pull request #148 from CheezeCake/documentation-fixes

Documentation fixes

Merge pull request #147 from susnux/master

Fixed .desktop and appdata file
Fix Face blocks position
Fix JOE magic number value

Fixed .desktop and appdata file

* Removed BOM from .desktop
* Set correct version in .desktop (version is the version of the Desktop
  Entry Specification not of the application)
* Set correct Icon name (the name should not contain an file extension)
* Removed invalid xml tag from appdata

GRAPHICS: Use const string array for shadow names.
Using a vector seems overkill here.

GRAPHICS: Update cached blend state when using default functions too.
They are not used by the implementation, but better safe than sorry.

GRAPHICS: Skip already culled draw list instead of breaking out.
Seems to have had no negative effect but was wrong nonetheless.

GRAPHICS: Move blend state tracking into gl wrapper
to avoid using static variables.
GRAPHICS: Move drawable attributes ids cache out of Drawable::GenRenderModelData.

GRAPHICS: Cache gl2 graphics pass info
to avoid processing GraphicsConfigPass every frame.
